Package com.twitter.common.service.registration

Interface Summary
ServerSet A server set provides real-time membership status of a set of servers.
ServerSetListener An interface to an object that is interested in receiving notification whenever the membership of a ServerSet changes.
 

Class Summary
Server An object of this class represents a server process that has joined a server set.
ZkServerSet This ServerSet implementation uses ZooKeeper to implement membership.
